## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="cb9b1-197">비동기 검색을 동시에 검색 결과 추가 하는 동안 검색으로 결과 표시할 수 있습니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cb9b1-197">An asynchronous search can show results as they are found while simultaneously searching for additional results.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="cb9b1-198">목록 상자 채우기 등의 작업에 유용 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cb9b1-198">This is useful for tasks such as populating list boxes.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="cb9b1-199">이 속성의 기본 설정은 `false`입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cb9b1-199">The default setting for this property is `false`.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="cb9b1-200">다음 C# 예제에서는 비동기 검색을 만드는 방법을 보여 줍니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cb9b1-200">The following C# example shows how to create an asynchronous search.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
using System.DirectoryServices;  
...  
// Bind to the users container.  
DirectoryEntry entry = new DirectoryEntry("LDAP://CN=users,DC=fabrikam,DC=com");  
// Create a DirectorySearcher object.  
DirectorySearcher mySearcher = new DirectorySearcher(entry);  
//Set the Asynchronous property to true.  
src.Asynchronous = true;  
//Use the FindAll method to get search results.  
SearchResultCollection res = src.FindAll();  
  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="cb9b1-204">이 속성에 설정 된 특성 멤버 등 managedBy 고유 이름 특성을 해야 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cb9b1-204">The attribute that this property is set to must be a distinguished name attribute, such as member or managedBy.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="cb9b1-205">단일 또는 다중 값 특성 수 있습니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cb9b1-205">The attribute can be either single or multi-valued.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="cb9b1-206">자세한 내용은 adschema 항목을 참조 하세요. "[멤버](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/default.asp?url=/library/en-us/adschema/adschema/a_member.asp)"및"[Managed By](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/default.asp?url=/library/en-us/adschema/adschema/a_managedby.asp)" MSDN library에서 [ http://msdn.microsoft.com/library ](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library)합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cb9b1-206">For more information, see the adschema topics "[Member](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/default.asp?url=/library/en-us/adschema/adschema/a_member.asp)" and "[Managed-By](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/default.asp?url=/library/en-us/adschema/adschema/a_managedby.asp)" in the MSDN Library at [http://msdn.microsoft.com/library](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library).</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="cb9b1-207">검색 기준 개체의 특성에 지정 된 고유 이름으로 식별 되는 개체에 대해 수행 됩니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cb9b1-207">The search is performed against the objects that are identified by the distinguished name that is specified in the attribute of the base object.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="cb9b1-208">예를 들어 기본 개체가 adschema 그룹 클래스 및 <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.AttributeScopeQuery%2A> 그룹의 구성원 인 모든 개체에 대 한 검색을 수행할지 "멤버"로 설정 됩니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cb9b1-208">For example, if the base object is an adschema group class and the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.AttributeScopeQuery%2A> is set to "member," then the search will be performed against all objects that are members of the group.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="cb9b1-209">자세한 내용은 MSDN library에서 adschema "그룹" 클래스 항목을 참조 [ http://msdn.microsoft.com/library ](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library)합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cb9b1-209">For more information, see the adschema "Group" class topic in the MSDN Library at [http://msdn.microsoft.com/library](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library).</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="cb9b1-210">경우는 <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.AttributeScopeQuery%2A> 속성을 사용 합니다 <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.SearchScope%2A> 속성으로 설정 되어 있어야 <xref:System.DirectoryServices.SearchScope.Base>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cb9b1-210">When the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.AttributeScopeQuery%2A> property is used, the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.SearchScope%2A> property must be set to <xref:System.DirectoryServices.SearchScope.Base>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="cb9b1-211">경우는 <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.SearchScope%2A> 설정, 다른 값으로 설정 합니다 <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.AttributeScopeQuery%2A> 속성이 throw 됩니다는 <xref:System.ArgumentException>합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cb9b1-211">If the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.SearchScope%2A> property is set to any other value, setting the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.AttributeScopeQuery%2A> property will throw an <xref:System.ArgumentException>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="cb9b1-212">자세한 내용은 MSDN library에서 "수행 하는 특성 범위 쿼리" 항목을 참조 하세요 [ http://msdn.microsoft.com/library ](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library)).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cb9b1-212">For more information, see the "Performing an Attribute Scope Query" topic in the MSDN Library at [http://msdn.microsoft.com/library](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library)).</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="cb9b1-213">다음 예제에서는 사용 하는 방법을 보여 줍니다는 <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.AttributeScopeQuery%2A> 속성 그룹의 멤버를 가져올 멤버 특성을 사용 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cb9b1-213">The following example shows how to use the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.AttributeScopeQuery%2A> property with the member attribute to get the members of a group.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="cb9b1-214">그런 다음 멤버 및 해당 전화 번호의 첫 번째 및 마지막 이름을 인쇄 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cb9b1-214">It then prints out the first and last names of the members and their telephone numbers.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
using System.DirectoryServices;  
DirectoryEntry group = new DirectoryEntry("LDAP://CN=MyGroup, …");  
DirectorySearcher src = new DirectorySearcher(group "(&(objectClass=user)(objectCategory=Person))");  
src.AttributeScopedQuery = "member";  
src.PropertiesToLoad.Add("sn");  
src.PropertiesToLoad.Add("givenName");  
src.PropertiesToLoad.Add("telephoneNumber");  
foreach(SearchResult res in src.FindAll())  
{  
    Console.WriteLine("…");  
}  
```

  
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="cb9b1-232">다음 C# 예제를 설정 하는 방법을 보여 줍니다 합니다 <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.DerefAlias%2A> 속성을 <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DereferenceAlias.Always> 는 기본 개체를 검색 하 고 찾을 때 별칭을 역참조 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cb9b1-232">The following C# example shows how to set the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.DerefAlias%2A> property to <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DereferenceAlias.Always> , so that it dereferences aliases when both searching subordinates and locating base objects.</span></span>  
  
```  
using System.DirectoryServices;  
...  
// Bind to the users container.  
DirectoryEntry entry = new DirectoryEntry("LDAP://CN=users,DC=fabrikam,DC=com");  
// Create a DirectorySearcher object.  
DirectorySearcher mySearcher = new DirectorySearcher(entry);  
// Set DerefAlias to Always.  
src.DerefAlias = DerefenceAlias.Always;  
//Use the FindAll method to get search results.  
SearchResultCollection res = src.FindAll();  
  
```

  
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="cb9b1-242">다음 예제에서는 16 진수 형식의 고유 이름의 컬렉션을 반환 하는 방법을 보여 줍니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cb9b1-242">The following example shows how to return a collection of distinguished names in hexadecimal format.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
using System.DirectoryServices;  
...  
DirectorySearcher src = new DirectorySearcher("…");  
src.PropertiesToLoad = new string[] {ntSecurityDescriptor,…};  
src.ExtendedDN = ExtendedDN.HexString;  
SearchResultCollection res = src.FindAll();  
  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="cb9b1-303">하는 경우 <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.SearchRoot%2A> 가 null 참조 (`Nothing` Visual basic에서), 검색 루트 서버는 현재 사용 중인 도메인의 루트에 설정 됩니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cb9b1-303">If <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.SearchRoot%2A> is a null reference (`Nothing` in Visual Basic), the search root is set to the root of the domain that your server is currently using.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="cb9b1-304">글로벌 카탈로그에서 검색 하는 방법은 여러 가지가 있습니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cb9b1-304">There are several ways to search in the global catalog:</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="cb9b1-305">글로벌 카탈로그를 열거 하 고 첫 번째 자식을 선택 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cb9b1-305">Enumerate the global catalog and pick the first child.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="cb9b1-306">서버 이름을 지정 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cb9b1-306">Specify the server name.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="cb9b1-307">DsGetDcName 함수를 사용 하 여 글로벌 카탈로그를 찾으려고 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cb9b1-307">Use the DsGetDcName function to find the global catalog.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="cb9b1-308">DsGetDcName 함수에 대 한 자세한 내용은 MSDN library에서 "DsGetDcName" 항목을 참조 [ http://msdn.microsoft.com/library ](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library)합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cb9b1-308">For more information on the DsGetDcName function, see the topic "DsGetDcName" in the MSDN Library at [http://msdn.microsoft.com/library](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library).</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="cb9b1-309">글로벌 카탈로그의 RootDSE 가져와 "rootNamingContext" 요청 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cb9b1-309">Get the RootDSE  of the global catalog and ask for "rootNamingContext".</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="cb9b1-310">LDAP를 사용 하는 경우에 따라 검색 경로 지정 하는 글로벌 카탈로그를 사용 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cb9b1-310">Use the global catalog, specifying a search path as if using LDAP.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="cb9b1-311">예를 들어, "GC: / / OU =..., DC =..., DC =..."입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cb9b1-311">For example, "GC://OU=..., DC=..., DC=...".</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="cb9b1-312">다음 C# 코드에는 글로벌 카탈로그를 열거 하 고 첫 번째 자식을 선택 하는 방법을 보여 줍니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cb9b1-312">The following C# code shows how to enumerate the global catalog and pick the first child.</span></span>  
  
    ```csharp  
    DirectoryEntry entry = new DirectoryEntry("GC://forestname");  
    IEnumerator ie = entry.Children.GetEnumerator();  
    ie.MoveNext();  
    entry = (DirectoryEntry)ie.Current;  
    DirectorySearcher search = new DirectorySearcher(entry);  
    ```

  
  
## Examples  
  
```csharp  
using System.DirectoryServices;  
...  
DirectorySearcher src = new DirectorySearcher("…");  
src.PropertiesToLoad = new string[] {ntSecurityDescriptor,…};  
src.SecurityMasks = SecurityMasks.Dacl | SecurityMasks.Owner;  
SearchResultCollection res = src.FindAll();  
  
```

  
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="cb9b1-350">다음 C# 예제를 설정 하는 방법을 보여 줍니다 합니다 <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.Tombstone%2A> 속성을 `true`입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="cb9b1-350">The following C# example shows how to set the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.Tombstone%2A> property to `true`.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
using System.DirectoryServices;  
...  
// Create a DirectorySearcher object.  
DirectorySearcher src = new DirectorySearcher("(isDeleted=true)");  
//Set the Tombstone property to true.  
src.Tombstone = true;  
//Use the FindAll method to get search results.  
SearchResultCollection res = src.FindAll();  
  
```
